data.displayName: Origin Business Go Variable (New and Moving Customers)

fees.description: A $68.00 (GST Incl) fee may apply when your property is reconnected (including when you move). Fee may vary.
A $68.00 (GST Incl) fee may apply when your property is disconnected (including when you move). Fee may vary.
A fee of $15.00 (GST exempt) may apply if your bill is not paid by the due date.
A 0.27% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by VISA debit card.
A 0.65% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by VISA credit card.
A 0.33% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by Mastercard debit card.
A 0.67% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by Mastercard credit card.
If you pay at an Australia Post outlet, a payment processing fee of the higher of $2.70 or 0.49% (incl GST) may apply.
A 0.64% fee (GST Incl) may apply to payments made by American Express credit card.

gasContract.terms: Not available all areas or property types. Small Business customers only. Visit originenergy.com.au/2889/Terms-and-conditions to find out more.
gasContract.variation: We may vary the Charges (including their amount, nature and structure) by notice to you at any time. The notice will be at least 5 business days prior to the effective date of the variation.

incentives.description: One credit per natural gas account. If this Origin Business Go Variable gas plan is still active with the customer on 30 January 2026, $300 (Incl. GST) credit will be applied to the customer's gas account after that date. If the customer ends this Origin Business Go Variable gas plan before that date, the customer will not receive any credit. Credit is not redeemable for cash.

eligibility.description: Offer only available to new business gas customers, and existing customers moving to a new property
Credit will only be applied if you haven't received a credit in the previous 12 months

gasContract.onExpiryDescription: At the end of the benefit period we may extend your current Energy Plan or set you up with a new Energy Plan, but only if we've written to you first and you haven't told us not to
gasContract.additionalFeeInformation: You must pay us any charges your distributor imposes on us in relation to services performed by your distributor (or anyone else) at your supply address. For details on additional charges that may apply see www.originenergy.com.au/2402/Additional-charges
